markets.title: Will Trump meet with Volodomyr Zelenskyy before 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If the President of the United States meets Volodomyr Zelenskyy in Mar 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: NOTE: A phone call will not count to resolve a market to Yes. A meeting will be included if the President and Volodomyr Zelenskyy shake hands or speak to each other directly; the President merely attending the same conference or event as Volodomyr Zelenskyy is not sufficient to resolve the market to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
